# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:投資或買賣時，為咗避免更大嘅損失而及時止損、賣出或停手（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop trading to avoid further losses
<eg>
yue:股價跌到咁低，我即刻止蝕。 (gu2 gaa3 gaa1 haa1 dou3 gam3 dai1, ngo5 zik1 hak1 zi2 sik1.)
eng:I cut my losses immediately as the stock price fell so low.

<eg>
yue:止蝕要夠狠，唔好拖拖拉拉。 (zi2 sik1 jiu3 gau3 han2, m4 hou2 to1 to1 laai4 laai4.)
eng:You need to be decisive when cutting losses; don't hesitate. [end of text]


